ActPilotage Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Transport of JOHN PATRICK MCCANN of Dartmouth, Nova Scotia, to be a member and part-time Vice-Chairperson of the Atlantic Pilotage Authority, to hold office during pleasure for a term ending December 13, 2021, in the place of Alexander Laughlin MacIntyre, whose term has expired.
